title: Episode 296: 10 Day Countdown (Feat. Tokyo Jetz)
itunes:title: Episode 296: 10 Day Countdown (Feat. Tokyo Jetz)
description:
Rapper, Tokyo Jetz joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote her new album "Cancel Culture." Tokyo opens up about the struggles she faced after she regretfully made a George Floyd 'joke' on social media, which ultimately led to the name of her album. On a lighter side, Tokyo speaks on how she's been celibate for over 2 years, and how that dry spell will be ending within the next 10 days. Jetz and the ladies discuss snooping around with men they know they shouldn't be with, guys shooting their shot at Tokyo while she was pregnant, and much more. Enjoy!
